<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer-pages.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="footer-page">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="footer-page-content">
        <div class="footer-page-hero">
            <h1><i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i> Latest News & Updates</h1>
            <p>Stay informed with the latest news, tips, and insights from the luxury car rental world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-page-section">
            <h2>Recent Articles</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">The Ultimate Guide to Luxury Car Rentals</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Discover everything you need to know about renting premium vehicles, from booking tips to driving etiquette. Learn how to make the most of your luxury car rental experience.</div>
                <p style="color: #ffd23f; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Published: January 15, 2025</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">New Fleet Additions: 2025 BMW M Series</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">We're excited to announce the addition of the latest BMW M5 Competition and M8 Coupe to our premium fleet. Experience unparalleled performance and luxury.</div>
                <p style="color: #ffd23f; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Published: January 10, 2025</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">Top 5 Driving Routes for Your Luxury Car Adventure</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Explore the most scenic and exciting driving routes perfect for luxury vehicles. From coastal highways to mountain passes, discover your next adventure.</div>
                <p style="color: #ffd23f; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Published: January 5, 2025</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">Holiday Special: Extended Rental Packages</div>
                <div class="faq-answer">Take advantage of our special holiday offers with extended rental packages. Perfect for long trips and special occasions with exclusive discounts.</div>
                <p style="color: #ffd23f; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">Published: December 20, 2024</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-page-section">
            <h2>Categories</h2>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-car-side"></i>
                    <h4>Vehicle Reviews</h4>
                    <p>In-depth reviews of our luxury fleet</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
                    <h4>Travel Guides</h4>
                    <p>Best destinations for luxury car trips</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-tools"></i>
                    <h4>Maintenance Tips</h4>
                    <p>Keep your luxury vehicle in top condition</p>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-tag"></i>
                    <h4>Special Offers</h4>
                    <p>Latest deals and promotions</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-page-section">
            <h2>Subscribe to Our Newsletter</h2>
            <p>Get the latest articles, car reviews, and exclusive offers delivered to your inbox.</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" style="padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #ffd23f; background: rgba(24, 24, 24, 0.8); color: #fff; width: 250px; margin-right: 1rem;">
                <button class="btn-cta" style="margin: 0; display: inline-flex;">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    Subscribe
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-page-cta">
            <a href="/" class="btn-cta">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                Back to Home
            </a>
            <a href="/fleet" class="btn-cta btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-car"></i>
                View Our Fleet
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="/js/mobileNav.js"></script>
</body>
</html>